    {
      "id": "37",
      "name": "Propriétés",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Source",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tutoriel",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Une fois le défi commencé, Arlecchino utilisera sa faux et ses pouvoirs spéciaux pour vous attaquer.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Les attaques d'Arlecchino sont imprévisibles. Soyez prudent si elle apparait soudainement devant vous !",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/7d8e66df06477b1d2646337697f9e0e5_2926090844295483944.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#8a6d48"
                      ],
                      "text": "Mécanique de base",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Lorsque les PV d'Arlecchino tombent à un certain niveau, elle se déplace au centre du champ de bataille et déclenche sa compétence pour appliquer un engagement vital à tous les personnages sur le terrain.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/1748913fbb589dc0c6dbe920cb894efc_3344566917619827368.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dans les combats suivants, certaines attaques d'Arlecchino consommeront ses propres PV. Lorsque ces attaques touchent un personnage, elles pourront restaurer les PV d'Arlecchino et appliquer un engagement vital au personnage.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Si un personnage touché est déjà sous l'effet d'un engagement vital, les DGT infligés par ces attaques augmentent davantage.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/07907c6caf4f03dd565ecafe835a97b9_4107252231907158099.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "italic"
                      ],
                      "text": "Dans certaines circonstances spécifiques, lorsque Arlecchino est attaquée et qu'elle est éloignée du personnage, ces attaques ne lui infligent aucun DGT.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/1645773abd16190f77f5161d66e7c1c7_4519026613536587280.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#8a6d48"
                      ],
                      "text": "Mécanique spéciale",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "En combat, certaines attaques d'Arlecchino appliqueront un",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "engagement vital",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "au personnage. Tant que l'engagement vital est actif, le personnage",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "subit des DGT de façon continue",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/a84022968224e02a1fbea0849390919e_2309212814583550912.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "L'engagement vital absorbera les effets de soins reçus par un personnage, ce qui l'empêchera de récupérer des PV. Une fois que ce personnage a été soigné pour une valeur égale à l'engagement vital, ce dernier disparait. Après l'élimination de l'engagement vital, une",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "icône de plume",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "apparaît autour du personnage.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/4f6c5e84a94643bbfb09bc789652f47c_6477228680131499653.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Lorsqu'un icône de plume apparaît autour du personnage, la prochaine",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "attaque chargée",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "des personnages de l'équipe qui touche Arlecchino déclenche une puissante marée nocturne écarlate qui peut",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "interrompre",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "certaines attaques d'Arlecchino, y compris son",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "banquet rouge sang",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", et inflige des DGT importants à Arlecchino.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/25/29705491/a3322d413a30e7e64c22e638f367eb54_4859226418999367267.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ff9999"
                      ],
                      "text": "Banquet rouge sang",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "En combat, Arlecchino déclenche aléatoirement diverses formes de banquet rouge sang, infligeant des DGT importants.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
